    "longBusinessSummary": "Binh Dien Fertilizer Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and trades in fertilizer products in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers NPK, NPK+TE, specialized, organic and bio-organic, and leaf fertilizers; microbiology and micronutrient products; growth regulators for plants and animals; and cattle feed and aqua products. It is also involved in producing, processing, and packaging of insecticides; and import and export of fertilizers, fertilizer production equipment and technology, agricultural machinery, and various plant and agricultural products. In addition, the company trades in real estate properties, such as housing and offices; and leases warehouses. Further, it engages in sports and advertising activities. The company exports its products. Binh Dien Fertilizer Joint Stock Company was founded in 1973 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
